A simple analogy

Imagine OpenAI as a car designer.

OpenAI designs the engine (AI models).
Microsoft provides a huge factory and power supply (cloud infrastructure).
Millions of people drive the finished car (ChatGPT).

OpenAI is the organization that invents and improves the AI itself, while partners like Microsoft help provide the enormous computing resources 
needed to train and deliver it to users around the world.

